{"tid":1434850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家要將焦點放番落五大訴求到！！","createTime":"2019-08-09T01:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T05:03:59.000Z","uid":239873,"like":96,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"998ded3c2453f81e733bffa5264a6d086532416c","tid":1434850,"uid":239873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:40:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>雖然哩段時間班警賊係好仆街<br />\n做盡晒喪盡天良既事<br />\n但大家要記得五大訴求先係我地最最最需要既野<br />\n政府依家根本就係想將視線全部轉移落警黑到<br />\n五好淨係不斷放大黑警濫權哩點<br />\n勿忘初心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1. 徹底撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n3. 必不追究反送中抗爭者<br />\n4. 成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴及元朗暴力事件<br />\n5. 全面落實雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c5a56edc77cceffa222bccc6e3698750dd2d9420","tid":1434850,"uid":239873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:41:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85c450a49c3c1242ab5cc6683eb148941912e051","tid":1434850,"uid":239873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:41:17.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"1c90b59d8f8a5c08121812a357f1487687d5c335","tid":1434850,"uid":239873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:41:27.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"74bd46d5c68c028ef6b23e1cdb7eec6e74337a0b","tid":1434850,"uid":239873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:41:43.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"dd573bb9c878f37ff31b07d44c34c0b69463a715","tid":1434850,"uid":239873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:41:57.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"ace04dc02ea34a621beaa560df0c8e84b74f95cc","tid":1434850,"uid":239873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited