66753","tid":1434850,"uid":239873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:27:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8d526bfa2e3ba07b51f73c1b15801cc8f1d5d70","tid":1434850,"uid":239873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:27:59.000Z","msg":"做咩負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講得唔岩出黎傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e31bd0d1a4ca3fc57a20398adeac7feb25388e","tid":1434850,"uid":239873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"082930b9c4fc6af3f1d77314965467242afdfc97","tid":1434850,"uid":239873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:50:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1. 徹底撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n3. 不追究612至今反送中抗爭者<br />\n4. 成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴及元朗暴力事件<br />\n5. 全面落實雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:29:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1. 徹底撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n3. 不追究612至今反送中抗爭者<br />\n4. 成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴及元朗暴力事件<br />\n5. 全面落實雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</ins><br />\n<br />\n大家要將焦點放番落五大訴求到！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434850</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d8a521b4e9c3cd494195fb309247fdf82de573d6","tid":1434850,"uid":22011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"736367f819bccd2aba1b2ae6067fec959a527e89","tid":1434850,"uid":239873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:14:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3360f970b9a0097e10ad2ea5f088d001bc78604b","tid":1434850,"uid":300602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:15:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"734b333203f618a35986cfcbcd725f6761c369af","tid":1434850,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:18:39.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雙普選設時限，為港獨正名，不能無了期五大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434739</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年之前！"},{"pid":"0fb73a98c557aa0f37467cc232197cec328f8d30","tid":1434850,"uid":36592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:24:16.000Z","msg":"借個位，全世界一齊推爆呢兩條民間記者會媽媽嘅分享！！我哋要全面收復民意！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434952/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434952/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黃大仙媽媽街坊講述8月3日與女兒回家被警察恐嚇經過</span></strong><br />\nYoutube: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zPoenzjYIrU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzPoenzjYIrU&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=4dfdd373\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zPoenzjYIrU</a><br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100040461427789/videos/103503131008401/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100040461427789%2Fvideos%2F103503131008401%2F&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=4a98884f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100040461427789/videos/103503131008401/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">深水埗準媽媽街坊講述8月6日警方在深水埗發射催淚彈的可怕經驗</span></strong><br />\nYoutube: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pqms6imibDE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dpqms6imibDE&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=1ac44042\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pqms6imibDE</a><br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100040461427789/videos/103503611008353/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100040461427789%2Fvideos%2F103503611008353%2F&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=15caf2a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100040461427789/videos/103503611008353/</a>"},{"pid":"e17d11577afe28059a2a54cfa90fb053c0827bbf","tid":1434850,"uid":11436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:56:52.000Z","msg":"撤回<s